:: Choose Archetype [cluster2 template choose-one]
When something important is unfolding, people fall into recognizable roles.

The eight archetypes map to how you tend to move through situations. Each has a distinct approach to obstacles, collaboration, and growth.

Read about each archetype before choosing. You can always return to this list.

