[[Continue|Declare Your Vector]]

:: Declare Your Vector [cluster3 passage]
You're now visible inside the campaign.

Different players are already moving.

Some are helping secure the resources that keep the residency running.
Some are organizing collaborators into coordinated action.
Some are helping the story travel further.
Some are stepping directly into active quests.

Every player chooses where their energy enters the system.

[[Choose your Intended Impact|Choose Intended Impact]]

:: Choose Intended Impact [cluster3 choose-one]
Where does your attention want to move?

Each domain shapes which quests you'll see. Read the summaries below, or [learn more about allyship domains](/wiki/domains).

**Gathering Resources** — Additive; accessing emotional energy; inner and outer resources. *"I want to help people access what they need."*

**Direct Action** — Action needs doing; removing obstacles. *"I want to get things done when something is blocking progress."*

**Raise Awareness** — Helping people see there is a higher level to operate at. *"I want to help others see what's possible."*

**Skillful Organizing** — Coordinating efforts; creating structures (external and internal). *"I want to bring people and systems into alignment."*

[[Gather Resources|Impact_GatherResources]]
[[Skillful Organizing|Impact_SkillfulOrganizing]]
[[Raise Awareness|Impact_RaiseAwareness]]
[[Direct Action|Impact_DirectAction]]

