:: Onboarding Complete [cluster3 result emits:bar_created intended_impact_bar_attached onboarding_completed]
Your presence is now part of the system.

The campaign knows who you are, how you tend to move, and where your energy wants to go.

From here, the next quests can connect your intention with real opportunities inside the residency.

[[Begin play|First Quest Stub]]

:: First Quest Stub [post-onboarding stub]
Your first quests await on the dashboard.

After you sign in, you'll see **Strengthen the Residency** and other starter quests tailored to your path. Choose your first move:

• **Strengthen the Residency** — Contribute support, invite an ally, share feedback, or share the campaign
• **Invite an Ally** — Bring someone aligned into the story
• **Offer a Skill or Resource** — Share what you have to give
• **Share the Campaign** — Help the story travel further
• **Contribute Financially** — Support the residency directly
• **Submit Feedback** — Shape the system through your experience

[[Begin play|BeginPlay]]

